    <abstract>
      <t>Many networks configure the link metric relative to the link capacity. High bandwidth traffic gets routed as per the link capacity. Flexible algorithms provides mechanisms to create constraint based paths in IGP. This draft documents a set of bandwidth related constraints to be used in Flexible Algorithms.</t>
